(167, 1, '2017-10-04 07:00:49', '2017-10-04 07:00:49', 'We offer the highest possible level of service, and provide Onsite Design Consultation and CAD drawings. We serve Virginia, and surrounding areas.\r\n<div class=\"col span_9_of_12\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #5f1b1a;\">Elegant Wine Storage</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Store your fine wines the way they are meant to be stored â in a beautiful traditional or contemporary wine cellar from Harvest Custom Wine Cellars and Saunas. Whether you are a homeowner, builder, architect, or interior designer, our team will work closely with you to create the perfect showcase for your collection.\r\n\r\n\r\nWe know that protecting your investment is a requirement. We size the appropriate cooling system for your wine cellar based on the cubic square feet, along with many other considerations.\r\n\r\n\r\nA Wine Cellar Project is typically between $20,000 and $500,000, and we work hard to stay within your budget.\r\n\r\n\r\nContact us today for a personal consultation, and see why we are true experts in design and installation. We also offer on-site design and CAD drawings.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_3_of_12\"><img class=\"img-2-col\" style=\"float: right;\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057641.png\" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #5f1b1a; text-align: center;\">Wine Cellar Gallery</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\"><img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057419.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Traditional Meets Contemporary</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">Wine Cellar Island</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\"><img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057420.p