(207, 1, '2017-10-05 02:27:36', '2017-10-05 02:27:36', 'We offer the highest possible level of service, and provide Onsite Design Consultation and CAD drawings. We serve Virginia, and surrounding areas.\r\n<div class=\"col span_9_of_12\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #5f1b1a;\">Elegant Wine Storage</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Store your fine wines the way they are meant to be stored â in a beautiful traditional or contemporary wine cellar from Harvest Custom Wine Cellars and Saunas. Whether you are a homeowner, builder, architect, or interior designer, our team will work closely with you to create the perfect showcase for your collection.</p>\r\nWe know that protecting your investment is a requirement. We size the appropriate cooling system for your wine cellar based on the cubic square feet, along with many other considerations.\r\n\r\nA Wine Cellar Project is typically between $20,000 and $500,000, and we work hard to stay within your budget.\r\n\r\nContact us today for a personal consultation, and see why we are true experts in design and installation. We also offer on-site design and CAD drawings.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_3_of_12\"><img class=\"img-2-col\" style=\"float: right;\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057641.png\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<br style=\"clear:both;\"/>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #5f1b1a; text-align: center;\">Wine Cellar Gallery</h2>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057419.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Traditional Meets Contemporary</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">Wine Cellar Island</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057420.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Wine Cellar</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">With lighting and display rows</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057421.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Arch Cellar Door</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">With Wine Cellar Ladder</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057422.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Contemporary Wine Racking</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">With High Display Rows</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057423.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Contemporary Wine Racking</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">Label Forward Display</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057424.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Wood Wine Racking</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">With Island and Neck Out Display</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057426.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Stone Inlay Arch Display</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">\"Hidden Wine Glasses\"</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057427.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Wine Cellar with many Architectural Features</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">Diamond Bins, Cellar Countertops, Bulk Bin Storage</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col span_4_of_12 block-gallery\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-center gallery-img\" src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/124057425.png\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">High Display Row</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px;\">Features the next bottle to Cork!</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Work with a Wine Cellar Expert', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '49-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 02:27:36', '2017-10-05 02:27:36', '', 49, 'http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/2017/10/05/49-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(224, 1, '2017-10-05 04:27:44', '2017-10-05 04:27:44', '', 'cellar-cooling', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cellar-cooling', '', '', '2017-10-05 04:32:55', '2017-10-05 04:32:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/?post_type=bxslider&#038;p=224', 0, 'bxslider', '', 0),
(228, 1, '2017-10-05 04:54:31', '2017-10-05 04:54:31', '     <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> At Harvest, we like Wine Guardian because of the versatility and quality of the products that they offer for both residential and commercial applications\r\n                <br/><br/>\r\n                The Through-the-wall options have a sleek design and are perfect for smaller to medium size cellars and wine cabinets, and are relatively easy to install.  These units are visible in the cellar, so racking configuration is very important to consider in the design process if you are building a cellar. </p>\r\n                <br/>\r\n                <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-1.jpg\" class=\"img-center\"><br/>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Ducted and Split Systems come in a variety of types and configurations to support any size custom wine cellar.  Since these systems are normally installed outside of the cellar and ducted into the cellar, this allows for more room for bottle capacity and racking design options.</p>\r\n                <div class=\"col span_6_of_12\">\r\n                    <h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ducted System</h4>\r\n                    <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-2.jpg\" class=\"img-center\">\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col span_6_of_12\">\r\n                    <h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Split System</h4>\r\n                    <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-3.jpg\" class=\"img-center\">\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n                <br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" />\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wine Guardian products provide reliable temperature and humidification, low noise and vibration, making Wine Guardian the leader in the industry.</p>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A two year manufacturer warranty is provided, with an option to warranty the compressor for three additional years.</p>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trying to figure out the best system for your cellar?</strong>  The cubic sq/ft is not the only thing to keep in mind when purchasing a cooling system to protect your investment.  We factor in all considerations when sizing the cooling unit to ensure that the correct system is installed.\r\n                </p>', 'Cellar Cooling', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 04:54:31', '2017-10-05 04:54:31', '', 51, 'http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/2017/10/05/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(229, 1, '2017-10-05 04:55:11', '2017-10-05 04:55:11', '     <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> At Harvest, we like Wine Guardian because of the versatility and quality of the products that they offer for both residential and commercial applications\r\n                <br/><br/>\r\n                Thes Through-the-wall options have a sleek design and are perfect for smaller to medium size cellars and wine cabinets, and are relatively easy to install.  These units are visible in the cellar, so racking configuration is very important to consider in the design process if you are building a cellar. </p>\r\n                <br/>\r\n                <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-1.jpg\" class=\"img-center\"><br/>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Ducted and Split Systems come in a variety of types and configurations to support any size custom wine cellar.  Since these systems are normally installed outside of the cellar and ducted into the cellar, this allows for more room for bottle capacity and racking design options.</p>\r\n                <div class=\"col span_6_of_12\">\r\n                    <h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ducted System</h4>\r\n                    <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-2.jpg\" class=\"img-center\">\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col span_6_of_12\">\r\n                    <h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Split System</h4>\r\n                    <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-3.jpg\" class=\"img-center\">\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n                <br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" />\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wine Guardian products provide reliable temperature and humidification, low noise and vibration, making Wine Guardian the leader in the industry.</p>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A two year manufacturer warranty is provided, with an option to warranty the compressor for three additional years.</p>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trying to figure out the best system for your cellar?</strong>  The cubic sq/ft is not the only thing to keep in mind when purchasing a cooling system to protect your investment.  We factor in all considerations when sizing the cooling unit to ensure that the correct system is installed.\r\n                </p>', 'Cellar Cooling', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 04:55:11', '2017-10-05 04:55:11', '', 51, 'http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/2017/10/05/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(230, 1, '2017-10-05 04:55:20', '2017-10-05 04:55:20', '     <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> At Harvest, we like Wine Guardian because of the versatility and quality of the products that they offer for both residential and commercial applications\r\n                <br/><br/>\r\n                The Through-the-wall options have a sleek design and are perfect for smaller to medium size cellars and wine cabinets, and are relatively easy to install.  These units are visible in the cellar, so racking configuration is very important to consider in the design process if you are building a cellar. </p>\r\n                <br/>\r\n                <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-1.jpg\" class=\"img-center\"><br/>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Ducted and Split Systems come in a variety of types and configurations to support any size custom wine cellar.  Since these systems are normally installed outside of the cellar and ducted into the cellar, this allows for more room for bottle capacity and racking design options.</p>\r\n                <div class=\"col span_6_of_12\">\r\n                    <h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ducted System</h4>\r\n                    <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-2.jpg\" class=\"img-center\">\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col span_6_of_12\">\r\n                    <h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Split System</h4>\r\n                    <img src=\"http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/right-c-3.jpg\" class=\"img-center\">\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n                <br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" />\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wine Guardian products provide reliable temperature and humidification, low noise and vibration, making Wine Guardian the leader in the industry.</p>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A two year manufacturer warranty is provided, with an option to warranty the compressor for three additional years.</p>\r\n                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trying to figure out the best system for your cellar?</strong>  The cubic sq/ft is not the only thing to keep in mind when purchasing a cooling system to protect your investment.  We factor in all considerations when sizing the cooling unit to ensure that the correct system is installed.\r\n                </p>', 'Cellar Cooling', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 04:55:20', '2017-10-05 04:55:20', '', 51, 'http://localhost/tim/wordpress/harvest/2017/10/05/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
